# Skills City API

Stacks API is an API to manage Projects, Services and People.

## Hello API [/hello]

### Hello, world! [GET]

+ Response 200

        {"message": "Hello, World!"}

## Hello, buddy! [/hello/{name}]

+ Parameters
    + name: toto (required, string) - name of the person to greet

### Hello, Buddy!  [GET]

+ Response 200

        {"message": "Hello, toto!"}

